Description: This Fender G5 Roland Ready Stratocaster boasts Roland's guitar synth technology, and a pre-installed GK Divided pickup. Along with your classic Strat sounds, you have powerful synth processing power! The guitar features an alder body, "C" shaped maple neck with rosewood fingerboard, a 6-saddle vintage style tremolo bridge, and standard Fender tuners. You do not need an external processor with this Guitar, put batteries in the back, plug it in, dial the guitar you want - Tele, Les Paul, Acoustic, Sitar! the tuning you want - , standard, Drop, G etc ..and you are good to go. It's also a standard strat ...read reviews on the web. I prefer this model to the Variax Guitars.The guitar was bought new back in 2012, but used only a couple of times, aside from a small mark - see pic 6 - its in mint condition. It's set up as a hard tail - i'm not a whammy bar fan. To convert back, just remove the blocks from the tremolo - see pics - re-set it up and good to go. As it's set as a hard tail, the action is awesome! :) I will also include a SKB hard case - by far my favorite cases - this one is missing the handle. Whammy bar is not included - i never keep them! Weighs 8 pounds 11 ounces. I will only ship within USA
Title: Fender G-5 Roland Stratocaster Electric Guitar Black - MINT - with SKB Case
